  "2193590": {
    "name": "Madzik - Episode 1",
    "steam_appid": 2193590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3ce6dc7e10cb6c5e5c6292061e78bc2f.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3ce6dc7e10cb6c5e5c6292061e78bc2f.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3ce6dc7e10cb6c5e5c6292061e78bc2f.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Madzik是对80年代的充满活力和电动的致敬，让你沉浸在一个怀旧的王国，每一个音乐节拍和像素都闪耀着时代的精神。 <strong>在这个奇幻的砍杀冒险中，多月的力量既改变环境也改变敌人，每个转折处都带来了新的挑战。</strong><br><br><strong>你准备好利用这些天体力量并塑造你的命运了吗？</strong> 向左滑动变成一个残暴的坦克，或向右滑动变成一个强大而充满激情的施法者。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>英雄之间的流畅切换:</strong> 在Makino和Veroline之间瞬间切换。两者都是才华横溢的战士，一个能造成与他所受伤害相同的伤害，而另一个能瞬间中和并消灭群体。<br></li><li><strong>合作游戏:</strong> 通过Steam Remote Play Together组队，实时结合你们的努力。<br></li><li><strong>月食:</strong> 每个周期体验环境和敌人的动态变化，遇见太阳、冰、火和风暴的月亮。<br></li><li><strong>壮丽变形:</strong> 利用Madzik能量进化成你英雄的强大版本，获得新的力量和技能。<br></li><li><strong>复杂的Boss战:</strong> 在多阶段的复杂战斗中挑战神Fhum，考验你的策略、技能和耐力。<br></li><li><strong>多功能技能系统:</strong> 参与一个灵活的技能系统，提供各种技能以个性化你的游戏风格。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3023f6c4d10c66b6a62ec10cf9e75cf7.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3023f6c4d10c66b6a62ec10cf9e75cf7.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3023f6c4d10c66b6a62ec10cf9e75cf7.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索ZIKVERLÄND的丰富历史</strong></h2>几个世纪以来，Zikverländ在太阳神Zik的关注下繁荣昌盛。然而，背叛的法师Ahnglum通过开启古老的传送门引发混乱，释放出来自一个未知世界的月亮和怪物。这带来了Nightfalls，一种在不可预测的月食期间引发疯狂和变异的可怕瘟疫。<br><br><strong>现在英雄们被召唤来结束Nightfalls并击败Ahnglum。</strong> 开始一场史诗般的冒险，将和平与理智带回曾经宁静的Zikverländ。勇士们，站起来，结束黑暗吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3d47992fc329a849df9b2a3991c1e2c6.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3d47992fc329a849df9b2a3991c1e2c6.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/3d47992fc329a849df9b2a3991c1e2c6.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索你的英雄</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/49a586bfaf7c2ac1b3cbecc0f952da7a.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/49a586bfaf7c2ac1b3cbecc0f952da7a.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/49a586bfaf7c2ac1b3cbecc0f952da7a.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索翼熊Makino：一位近战中的强大力量，能够用他的魔法战锤冲入敌阵。</strong> 他能够承受大量打击，并在必要时造成巨大伤害。当Makino消耗Madzik能量时，他回归到动物本能，跳向敌人，用锋利的爪子撕裂他们。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/0a83478b149a502c901c8d87038fe0f9.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/0a83478b149a502c901c8d87038fe0f9.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/0a83478b149a502c901c8d87038fe0f9.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>外表可爱的Veroline是一位强大的法术施放者，准备摧毁任何挡在她路上的人。</strong> 她利用她的魔法能力控制战场并逃脱攻击者。当她被Madzik能量充满时，她拥抱自己的黑暗面，并获得一系列全新的技能，在敌人心中播下恐惧。<br><br>在这些强大的英雄之间切换，克服所有遇到的挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索神秘的土地</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/9f55df9218a2bda9965a955cedfb839d.poster.avif?t=1717681247\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/9f55df9218a2bda9965a955cedfb839d.webm?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/9f55df9218a2bda9965a955cedfb839d.mp4?t=1717681247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>踏上充满回报性探索机会的活力土地。从羊毛到铅笔，Zikverländ由现实世界的元素塑造，赋予游戏独特的外观。<br><br><strong>Madzik是一场难忘的冒险，月球疯狂、合作游戏和沉浸式叙事融合在一起，提供一种独特的体验。</strong><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>加拿大媒体基金的财务支持<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193590/extras/a93be716c704c66283e1b3c9c70a6866.webp?t=1717681247\" width=150 height=58 /></span>",
